<bibRefCitation id="8D17DCBDFFC6FFD6FDF4FDD3FC97741E" author="Van" box="[516,795,511,536]" pageId="13" pageNumber="40" refString="Van Steenis, J., Ricarte, A., Vujic, A., Birtele, D. &amp; Speight, M. C. D. (2016) Revision of the West-Palaearctic species of the tribe Cerioidini (Diptera, Syrphidae). Zootaxa, 4196 (2), 151 - 209." type="journal article" year="2016">
Van Steenis 
<emphasis id="DBF27D5EFFC6FFD6FD67FDD2FD40741E" box="[663,716,511,536]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="40">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
). A male of 
<taxonomicName id="2E86DACFFFC6FFD6FC44FDD3FBC4741E" box="[948,1096,512,536]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphiximorpha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="40" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="euprosopa">
<emphasis id="DBF27D5EFFC6FFD6FC44FDD3FC4E7411" box="[948,962,512,535]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="40">S</emphasis>
